                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321129-55-off314 t18321129-55-cd315"></join>, 2 silver sauce-ladles, value 50s.; 16 silver spoons, value 10l.; 1 coat, value 2l.; 2 waistcoats, value 10s.; 1 pair of breeches, value 10s.; 1 jacket, value 5s.; 1 pair of overalls, value 3s.; 1 hat, value 4s., and 1 pair of gaiters, value 2s., the goods of 
                     
